<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ decoy_site_title }}</title>
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, sans-serif;
    color: #2d3748; line-height: 1.7; background: #fff;
  }
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a365d 0%, #2b6cb0 100%);
    color: #fff; padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center;
  }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .hero p { font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.9; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .features {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px; padding: 64px 24px; max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .feature { text-align: center; }
  .feature .icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .feature h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #1a365d; }
  .feature p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #4a5568; }
  .footer {
    text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px; color: #a0aec0;
    font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="hero">
  <h1>{{ decoy_site_title }}</h1>
  <p>{{ decoy_site_tagline }}</p>
</div>
<div class="features">
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="icon">&#9881;</div>
    <h3>Infrastructure</h3>
    <p>Cloud architecture and deployment solutions tailored for your business needs.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="icon">&#128274;</div>
    <h3>Security</h3>
    <p>Comprehensive security audits and compliance frameworks to protect your data.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="feature">
    <div class="icon">&#128200;</div>
    <h3>Analytics</h3>
    <p>Data-driven insights and performance monitoring for informed decision-making.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="footer">
  &copy; {{ ansible_date_time.year }} {{ decoy_site_title }}. All rights reserved.
</div>
</body>
</html>
